public abstract class AbstractSeriesVisibilityDialog<T extends javax.swing.JPanel>
extends AbstractOkCancelDialog

This dialog permits the visibility of plot series to be changed, and allows subclasses to extend its functionality by adding series-related panes and behavior. Note that this class must be specialised at least by specifying the generic parameter. TODO: change the generic type to permit Void (set of types?)
